trans-unit.source: Key Vault C# Client API Reference
trans-unit.target: Key Vault C# Client API Reference

trans-unit.source: The Azure Key Vault C# Client API supports all the functionality of the Azure Key Vault programming model available through the REST API by wrapping these operations with C# methods so you can work with the Key Vault without needing to directly access the REST end point.
trans-unit.target: The Azure Key Vault C# Client API supports all the functionality of the Azure Key Vault programming model available through the REST API by wrapping these operations with C# methods so you can work with the Key Vault without needing to directly access the REST end point.
